    "Instead, we propose a unified taxonomy based on the unit test generation lifecycle.",
    "As illustrated in Fig. 4, we conceptually partition the generation process into a core generative engine supported by four distinct technical layers.",
    "This framework serves as the structural backbone for this survey.The foundation of this framework is the prompt-driven generation.",
    "This layer represents the central engine where the LLM operates, focusing on how the model is prompted to perform the task [103,122,161].",
